Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:05:01.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 等開學了你不想見也得見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是禍不單行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,受了一次挫折你就越來越懦弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:13.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,的確 輝夜大小姐曾度過的暑假都是悲慘的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:18.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這次暑假你一次都沒見到白銀會長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:23.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,從長遠來看 卻可以說是最佳選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:29.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,無法見面的時間將培育愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:33.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長現在和輝夜大小姐是同樣的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:38.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都思念得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都掰著手指數著還有多久暑假才能結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:49.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在此情此景下 要是能和輝夜大小姐來一場命運的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:53.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼他迄今為止積攢下來的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:57.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就會被一下子釋放出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:00.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 答得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,終於回到平時的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:05.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 今天有兩個本家的執事在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:10.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能毫無準備地從這裡逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,準備？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:35.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩去浜松町方向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:38.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,晚飯已經備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:43.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.14,0:06:46.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我在看煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,至少讓我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:50.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,講笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:05.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:16.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜同學她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可能已經到附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原學姐你就待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:30.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,您撥打的電話不在服務區或已關機 無法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:32.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:34.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為人太多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:37.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說我的手機太舊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:38.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:41.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 你是想去煙火大會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,因為交通管制 這附近是塞車了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,大概趕不上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:50.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,趕不上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可早坂都幫我到這一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:58.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我總是這麼慘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:02.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:03.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:06.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來的路程我靠自己走過去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:14.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心啊 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:15.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我們約在竹芝碼頭見面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.93,0:08:32.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,大路上人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:35.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,抄近道的話說不定能勉強趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.03,0:08:42.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能見到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:45.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,第一個我照顧的學弟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:49.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,第一個願意跟我交朋友的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,第一個喜歡上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:59.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我的生活 被他們所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:05.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是能和我喜歡的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.97,0:09:08.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一起眺望那場煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那該有多麼幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:13.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那該有多麼美好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:16.61,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這個暑假我的腦海中充斥著這些想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這個夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.21,0:09:24.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我不奢求什麼戀情與愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:32.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所以至少讓我和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,…已經結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:46.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,請您在離開時帶走垃圾與食品飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:48.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:53.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的煙火大會已經結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:10:01.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,請您在離開時帶走垃圾與食品飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:04.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這世上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:10.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他們有好好享受煙火了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:23.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要是那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:28.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我只從大樓縫隙間看到了煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但那麼大的煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.83,0:10:35.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他們看到的煙火一定很美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:41.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,大家能高興 我就滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:53.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想看啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:56.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,煙火…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:10:59.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:04.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那我帶去你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:07.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 四宮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼想看的話我就讓你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:18.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:23.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說「讀出四宮的想法然後找到四宮」的遊戲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:28.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和平時那些比起來 這個簡單一百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:35.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:39.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 車我弄來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,又是那個小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:43.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都坐上去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:51.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:02.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,司機 順著這條路上高速
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:04.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,從東京灣跨海隧道去海螢島那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.94,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有一場前幾天因為大雨延期的煙火大會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:11.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:12.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在千葉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:16.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,木更津的煙火大會到8點半才結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:20.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還有20分鐘能到千葉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:23.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 但是值得挑戰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:26.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會讓四宮看到煙火的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微加速一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不要告訴公司哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:37.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊這個帥呆了的司機
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:46.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊 保佑我們一定趕上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:53.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 完全看不見外面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,東京灣跨海隧道從海裡經過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:57.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,當然看不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,海螢島停車站的路牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:01.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要到地面上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:05.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:12.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:45.27,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都看向煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:49.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法從你的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:59.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,移開視線
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,心跳聲太大了 已經
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:17.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,聽不見煙火的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:23.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,新學期第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:28.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都帶著心中的憂愁和期待回到日常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:33.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在什麼事都沒能發生的漫長暑假的最後
