Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:45.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這個男人回想這些過程
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.73,0:14:48.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那我帶去你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:51.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:53.91,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,後悔得想死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:59.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說「讀出四宮的想法然後找到四宮」的遊戲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:02.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,羞恥羞恥羞恥羞恥羞恥羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:03.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這太羞恥了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,黑歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:14.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,經過了大半的暑假都不能見到輝夜的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:17.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白銀在煙火大會那天 遇到了輝夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:20.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白銀的情緒斷崖式上升
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:26.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,被高漲的情緒支配說出了很多羞恥的名言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.03,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,那我帶去你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:28.32,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說「讀出四宮的想法然後找到四宮」的遊戲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:31.59,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,和平時那些比起來 這個簡單一百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:35.02,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 但是值得挑戰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:38.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,出自 白銀御行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:44.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在今後十幾年想起來都會苦悶難堪的黑歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:48.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果現在和四宮見面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:52.61,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.62,0:15:55.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但你那天的話怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:58.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可以說非常自我陶醉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:03.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 真是羞恥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:06.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:09.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這學期也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:11.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？嗯…藤原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:13.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:27.34,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(50,0)\bord10\3c&HF5EEEF&\c&HA5558D&\b1}瞥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,裝作沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:33.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,已經認為我羞恥到不忍直視的地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮 之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.01,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(50,0)\bord10\3c&HF5EEEF&\c&HA5558D&\b1}瞥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:47.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真的搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:48.50,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有好多灰塵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:51.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得我羞恥到和我絕交了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:55.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 輝夜的確是在迴避白銀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:57.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這絕不是惡意的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:16:59.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,或者說 相反
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:03.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這是害羞和緊張引起的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:07.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,通俗來說是 喜歡的逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我避開了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:18.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣不就像是說我很在意會長嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:22.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,搭話吧 像暑假之前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要重建四宮的信賴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.68,0:17:28.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,自然的 開朗的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 先普通的打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:41.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,行進路線連成直線的兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:44.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一定可以開始對話的展開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:47.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:04.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同學 要先掃地才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:06.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這麼多灰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:13.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好難搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:15.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我負責這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:18.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人重整旗鼓再次挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:21.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然而結果還是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:26.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 接近了更沒辦法直視會長的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.37,0:18:29.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用什麼表情和四宮搭話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:32.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,每次都差一點的相互錯過的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:37.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就像是空中對戰的兩架戰鬥機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:41.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是兩次都錯過了實在太不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:42.84,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:48.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 會長在害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:52.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就沒有必要害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:54.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我很冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.97,0:18:55.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:58.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,下次絕對要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:00.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:13.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,星號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:19.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同學 你在把我當傻子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:22.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,請認真打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:25.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這遊戲到底是什麼規則
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.79,0:19:27.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,必須說話打破誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:29.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:32.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 不應該是星號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.46,0:19:33.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:38.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是Delta啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:45.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 連你也來搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我幹什麼了嗎我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:51.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你什麼都不懂啊石上君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼一上來就這麼鄙視我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:56.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,石上 我有那麼滑稽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:57.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,連會長都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:04.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 雖然不知道怎麼回事我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:06.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,石上墜機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪石上君礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同學也別礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:17.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:19.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原墜機
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才開始到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:26.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我躲著她很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:29.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是連四宮也這麼來來回回好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.88,0:20:32.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,難道她在在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要冷靜 閉上眼睛就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:44.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,難道我的行為並不是那麼羞恥 而是特別帥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:47.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白銀重新站起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:48.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,下一次 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:50.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,下次要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:07.54,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我…有話一定要和會長說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:10.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 煙火大會那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:17.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要說 對他說謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:24.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:28.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 煙火大會那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:33.79,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,羞恥羞恥羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是羞恥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:36.23,Kaguya_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,羞恥和疼同音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.47,0:21:41.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.94,0:21:43.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,白銀墜機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.71,0:21:46.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長我有話對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:50.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:52.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 會長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:56.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣回到了日常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:21:58.42,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,第二學期開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:11.97,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君と私　きっと今同じ気持ちだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:11.97,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}你和我 現在一定懷著同樣的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:34.50,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君から笑いかけてくれたなら　天使でいられるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:34.50,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}只要有你的微笑 我就還能如天使一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:40.79,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}気付いたの　試されてる　意地悪な駆け引きで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:40.79,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}已經注意到我在用壞心眼的謀略考驗他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:43.59,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}後にはもう引けないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:43.60,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}已經不能退縮了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:46.55,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}仕掛けてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.76,0:22:46.55,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}讓我給你設下圈套吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:53.68,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}さあ　掛かってみせて　戸惑ってみせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:53.68,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}來吧 掉進陷阱吧 不知所措吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:23:03.78,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}そして最後に伝えてみせて　好きだって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:23:03.78,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}然後在最後說出那句喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:11.45,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君と私　どんな風に恋するの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.86,0:23:11.45,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}你和我 將會怎樣相戀呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:15.33,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}探る RELATION
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:15.33,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}去探索 RELATION
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:22.96,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}余裕なんてないよ　見つめられる度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:22.96,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}每次被你注視 我一點都不從容哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:26.76,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}いつも震えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.09,0:23:26.76,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}我總是會顫抖著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:33.60,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}素直じゃない私を連れ出して！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:33.60,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}請帶走這樣不坦率的我！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:38.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛頭腦戰 這是無法坦誠相待的男女的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:40.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,心中無法說出口的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:45.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天他們也在期盼被告白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.31,0:23:48.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定讓你說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:52.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「喜歡」
